                <h3>DOUBLE-CROSSING THE BRIDGE: A TROLL HEIST</h3>
                <h4>Adult Satirical Fantasy</h4>
                <p>Three trolls walk into a bar … And plan the heist of the century. University didn’t prepare Granu to survive troll puberty, and when her students turn on her, she’s nearly made into a troll filet. Jobless and facing eviction, Granu is desperate to avoid taking a demeaning job in the tar pits. When her best friend, Kradduk, devises a plan to rob The Covered Bridge, the most powerful company in the city, Granu knows Kradduk’s going for it with or without her. She won’t let him end up the entrée in someone’s dinner spread. She gathers a crew of malcontent trolls and agrees to keep them out of the sun long enough to become filthy rich. That is, as long as the billy goats don’t get wind of the scheme.</p>
            </div>
