                <h3>THE KEY OF ARGOS</h3>
                <h4>Adult Epic Fantasy</h4>
                <p>Ronan Agnatha raises a rebellion to seize her rightful throne and avenge the slaughter of her family by the cruel and corrupt Magistratum. In her quest, she finds unexpected support from Gavin and James, a pair of untested forest men on their own journey to discover truth about magic. Their fates become entwined when the men join Ronan’s cause, but there is a darker threat looming, one they couldn’t anticipate.</p>
                <p>A legendary sorcerer intends to use Ronan, Gavin, and James in his own plot to free his deranged, powerful sister. Should he succeed, chaos and destruction will be the true rulers of Argos.
